The national assembly speaker Justin Muturi is slowly advancing his intentions in a fresh push to succeed President Uhuru Kenyatta as the mt Kenya spokesman. The speaker has over the last few days undergoing a strict cultural regimen in preparation for his coronation this Saturday&hellip;And as Ktns Daniel Kariuki reports, Muturi says he' is ready to take over the mantle even as his absence in a special sitting in parliament raised concern among some members.